
First:
ionic plugin add https://github.com/opuslogica/OLIRecorder
ionic platform add android

Then, when you edit the actual plugin source and need it incorporated in the app:
ionic plugin rm org.opuslogica.plugins.OLIRecorder
ionic plugin add https://github.com/opuslogica/OLIRecorder

To debug:
without your phone plugged in:

	ionic run ios

then start Safari, and from the Develop menu connect to the iOS Simulator -> index.html
Click "Start"
